data.description: ***DON'T MISS THIS GREAT OPPORTUNITY TO CREATE MEMORIES IN THIS WARM & FRIENDLY NEIGHBORHOOD*** - Come checkout this spacious and well-maintained, two-level home in the gated community of Cypress Crossing. Wood and solid ceramic tile flooring in the public areas. Great flow between the living room to the kitchen with its breakfast area. Separate dining room for special family dining moments. Large backyard for family fun and entertaining. Covered patio for relaxing outdoors. Large master bedroom and bath. All guest bedrooms are nice sizes on the upper level. An open bonus space on the second level. Generator for those unexpected times. Extra drive-way for your driving teenagers. Take a walk to the beautiful community park and have a family picnic. This community park is near a small lake.
